<h1>About</h1>

<p>A30Insurance application - Information</p>

<p class="bw"> Basic Features</p>
<p>
    The application allows you to register and update customer information. Then, claims
    can be filed, adjusted and paid. Medical, Dental, Vision and Drug claims can be filed.
    A row of actions appear after each claim. 
    You can use: claim (new claim), 
    Adjust or Pay the claim. Stay on returns you immediately 
    to the claim screen. Focus on positions at the operative claim.
</p>

<p class="bw">Style Feature</p>
<p> Styles can be used on claim and update screens: outline, solid, and picture backgrounds are available.</p>



